HEADWORD: Grazer
<hw>Graz"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One that grazes; a
creature which feeds on growing grass or herbage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The cackling goose,⟦br⟧
Close <qex>grazer</qex>, finds wherewith to ease her want.</q>
<rj><qau>J. Philips. </qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grazier</ent>⟦br⟧
